  "3090810": {
    "name": "Truckful / 乡野奇运",
    "steam_appid": 3090810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/8ae67df0d498de093a012e0658262ce1.avif?t=1772008127\" width=1080 height=418 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Truckful / 乡野奇运》是一款单人汽车送货冒险游戏，围绕为村民们完成各种送货任务而展开，你将一路探索，逐渐揭开附近古老森林的神秘面纱。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/fb88540388565103b77c62a1539ca4c4.avif?t=1772008127\" width=600 height=127 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/ef660825d6d171a6206466a577ee78c9.poster.avif?t=1772008127\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/ef660825d6d171a6206466a577ee78c9.webm?t=1772008127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/ef660825d6d171a6206466a577ee78c9.mp4?t=1772008127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开驾驶你的小货车穿越蜿蜒的乡间小路、尘土飞扬的低地和小镇。升级你的卡车，提高它的载货能力，让它能更快地穿越各种艰难的路线。让你的货斗里装满形状各异、摇摇晃晃的货物——无论是需要迅速送达的冻鱼，还是经典的考验真正驾驶实力的奶奶最爱的花瓶。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/87e971b3116a523e4e68e9c414573a8a.avif?t=1772008127\" width=600 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/5bd268618a10dfd2496d32024d21f7e0.poster.avif?t=1772008127\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/5bd268618a10dfd2496d32024d21f7e0.webm?t=1772008127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/5bd268618a10dfd2496d32024d21f7e0.mp4?t=1772008127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看这片看似宁静的乡村其实暗藏着无数秘密。隐秘的小径、雾气弥漫的湿地、严酷的沼泽以及尘土飞扬的流沙，仿佛都在诉说着过往的故事，静静等待着被揭示。探索各种地标及其周边环境，揭开密林树枝下被岁月掩埋的秘密。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/539e247a5c319782d367ca9089036ec1.avif?t=1772008127\" width=600 height=127 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/830d9cd4fc5732a16d09e3712e249e8b.poster.avif?t=1772008127\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/830d9cd4fc5732a16d09e3712e249e8b.webm?t=1772008127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/830d9cd4fc5732a16d09e3712e249e8b.mp4?t=1772008127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你要完成这些充满挑战的送货任务，你需要一件值得信赖的工具——一辆老旧但可靠的小货车。它配备宽大的货斗，可以将各种物资送达城镇居民手中。居民们会感激辛勤工作的你，并时常为你提供升级、废料收集等帮助。更重要的是他们提供的线索，将帮助你揭开这片神秘森林的终极谜团。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/170e53b79b5f69886486bf034b22419d.avif?t=1772008127\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/fadbe7d6739e8fe924c9043167e201a7.poster.avif?t=1772008127\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/fadbe7d6739e8fe924c9043167e201a7.webm?t=1772008127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090810/extras/fadbe7d6739e8fe924c9043167e201a7.mp4?t=1772008127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乡乡间边缘的这片古老森林对外来者并不友好，它的诡秘频频出现在当地的传说与神话之中，那潜伏在树影斑驳间带来的压迫感挥之不去。直面未知的挑战，终极谜底待你亲手揭开。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶、升级并定制你的小货车。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为你的货斗装满形状各异、大小不一的货物。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为有需要的村民运送货物。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受基于物理拟真的汽车驾驶体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开古老森林的神秘面纱。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 繁体中文, 简体中文, 日语, 韩语, 阿拉伯语, 保加利亚语, 捷克语, 丹麦语, 荷兰语, 芬兰语, 希腊语, 匈牙利语, 印度尼西亚语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 俄语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 瑞典语, 泰语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 越南语",
